      ],
      "combo_choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": 360853,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "The second step is a decarboxylation. Show the structure of the product and the mechanism of the decarboxylation reaction.",
      "answers": [],
      "hints": [],
      "formats": [
        "free-response"
      ],
      "combo_choices": []
    },
    {
      "id": 360854,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "The third step is hydrolysis of an imine to yield an amine and an aldehyde. Show the structures of both products and the mechanism of the hydrolysis reaction.",
